{"tid":1535611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人成日mean親人","createTime":"2019-09-03T12:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:50:29.000Z","uid":205534,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5b02fdaa2082450b65e2e1b5b25e98aba222b8","tid":1535611,"uid":205534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:06:20.000Z","msg":"講野太mean<br />\n句句都好似帶刺咁"},{"pid":"d9be72daca27e528bdeb77c9910b0efe0f3a985b","tid":1535611,"uid":205534,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:07:08.000Z","msg":"然後就比人討厭<br />\n其實唔係帶惡意去講<br />\n但係成日唔小心就講咗出口"},{"pid":"47cb9f19724dc3f455c05a5f396f63597bca35ac","tid":1535611,"uid":249721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:08:50.000Z","msg":"有個fd講野mean得黎好笑 咁樣會冇咁黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b2b802da68408c702d0237d32257431f7f9668","tid":1535611,"uid":51540,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"我都好mean但人地係鍾意我mean<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講野直都唔等於可以冇禮貌 冇分寸<br />\n咩性格都好 講嘢要識分場合同對象<br />\n我mean人嘅低線係絕對唔會無啦啦人身攻擊/恥笑或者歧視人地 <br />\n笑人地本身條件差呢d更加係唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmean嘅精粹係一針見血咁講出一件事嘅本質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係特登串人"},{"pid":"cbd0141fa955505a3c170ec270103b5b6bc2e7fa","tid":1535611,"uid":113546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:59:22.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<br />\n其實你冇必要照顧啲玻璃心 識睇場合同埋諗過點解果時要做自己 mean人嘅目的就得啦<br />\n<br />\n例如你去人地婚宴 條女出晒名係公廁但仲扮晒上菜咁<br />\n咁咪串鳩佢囉<br />\n睇佢敢怒不敢言 怕發脾氣就有可能破壞自己嘅婚宴<br />\n咁咪仲過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喱個世上總有那麼多的垃圾廢人<br />\n奸唔起壞唔起就話自己乖 安守本份<br />\n事實係連玩嘅份都冇喱啲人份<br />\n遇到喱啲廢柴 mean9佢地當撚鳩啲垃圾 不知幾好玩<br />\n你咁做係幫緊個社會清理垃圾<br />\n等佢地安全本份 做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750af6c8ed650da7197a10047ba441a9342fe246","tid":1535611,"uid":119041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:09:45.000Z","msg":"mean到EX覺得我串....成日放箭....<br />\n但朋友又覺得無問題"},{"pid":"1635c666d4de6873d3cfe94c923596440e8cf8b5","tid":1535611,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:19:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25cbdda90c2dddbadf77f3bab15886457b837d01","tid":1535611,"uid":236175,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"要拿捏得好先唔會令人反感<br />\n好笑同討厭真係一線之差"},{"pid":"0bab91c113068464d04278d99d8935c7f78a54dc","tid":1535611,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:05:09.000Z","msg":"突然諗返菲律賓人質事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536383</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3541e2afb63b88a6cb67dd7f1e25c2c2e437fcd8","tid":1535611,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87b2b802da68408c702d0237d32257431f7f9668","tid":1535611,"uid":51540,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"我都好mean但人地係鍾意我mean<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講野直都唔等於可以冇禮貌 冇分寸<br />\n咩性格都好 講嘢要識分場合同對象<br />\n我mean人嘅低線係絕對唔會無啦啦人身攻擊/恥笑或者歧視人地 <br />\n笑人地本身條件差呢d更加係唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmean嘅精粹係一針見血咁講出一件事嘅本質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係特登串人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:05:52.000Z","msg":"最鐘意比人mean <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedae8404c177d30220a06b95f8d3d6ecd5866ad","tid":1535611,"uid":311602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87b2b802da68408c702d0237d32257431f7f9668","tid":1535611,"uid":51540,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"我都好mean但人地係鍾意我mean<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\